trt_name: The first sampling events occurred immediately after fertilizer application and on the day after, whereas the following sampling events in the first month of the experiment were spaced first by 2 days and later by 3 days. After the first month, sampling became less frequent and occurred about once every 3 weeks. The last four sampling events of the experiment were spaced by 40-day intervals.
